307
00:18:07,850 --> 00:18:10,640
So you just live your life.

308
00:18:10,700 --> 00:18:14,200
Don't feel sorry or guilty about me.

309
00:18:14,446 --> 00:18:17,004
Let's just be strangers.

310
00:18:18,700 --> 00:18:21,400
By chance...

311
00:18:21,700 --> 00:18:23,900
Are you seeing someone?

312
00:18:23,907 --> 00:18:25,504
Is that why you're so cold?

313
00:18:25,504 --> 00:18:28,370
Why do I have to explain that to you?

314
00:18:30,368 --> 00:18:32,919
It doesn't concern you.

315
00:18:33,888 --> 00:18:35,722
Mind your own business.

316
00:18:52,823 --> 00:18:56,650
That's it for today's lesson.

317
00:19:13,061 --> 00:19:15,228
