318
00:19:21,994 --> 00:19:25,381
Sorry about early.

319
00:19:25,381 --> 00:19:27,591
For being mean to you.

320
00:19:30,345 --> 00:19:31,779
It's okay.

321
00:19:31,779 --> 00:19:34,340
I like it.

322
00:19:35,767 --> 00:19:37,292
What?

323
00:19:37,292 --> 00:19:39,662
