324
00:19:39,662 --> 00:19:41,956
But now we're even.

325
00:19:43,716 --> 00:19:46,852
I made a mistake while I was drunk.

326
00:19:46,852 --> 00:19:50,488
Let's call it even with this. Deal?

327
00:19:52,699 --> 00:19:54,626
Deal.

328
00:19:59,707 --> 00:20:02,751
