329
00:20:02,751 --> 00:20:07,704
People get angry when they are angry,

330
00:20:07,704 --> 00:20:10,449
but sometimes also when they're sad

331
00:20:10,449 --> 00:20:12,561
because they don't want to cry.

332
00:20:12,561 --> 00:20:14,538
I said go.

333
00:20:16,933 --> 00:20:21,320
You were really furious back there.

334
00:20:27,802 --> 00:20:30,345
This is my place.

335
00:20:33,849 --> 00:20:35,467
