338
00:20:40,006 --> 00:20:41,573
Is that so?

339
00:20:41,573 --> 00:20:43,342
Maybe he moved?

340
00:20:43,342 --> 00:20:46,794
Before I went to the military, my friend used to live in Room 403.

341
00:20:46,794 --> 00:20:47,972
Oh really?

342
00:20:47,972 --> 00:20:49,824
